title: Un Village Francais (A French Village) - season 4 (Eng subs)
description: Un Village Francais (A French Village) - season 4 This acclaimed drama is about the German occupation of France during World War II, and its effects on the inhabitants of a small village in Jura. In June 1940, the village of Villeneuve awakes to the arrival of the German army - and the next four years of occupation have a shattering effect on the lives of all its inhabitants.
